{"tid":2317063,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"出席記者會疑反轉口罩佩戴　陳肇始被追問沒回應","createTime":"2020-12-08T09:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T03:08:14.000Z","uid":291865,"like":49,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"6a38edb7ad7ad478c41752efd02344e11f46fb5b","tid":2317063,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:52:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1564220_2_20201208165351.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1564220_2_20201208165351.jpg&h=d6098606&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局局長陳肇始下午出席記者會期間，被傳媒發現，相信將口罩反轉了佩戴。<br />\n<br />\n她在記者會被問到是否將口罩前後反轉了時，以手觸摸口罩，並無作出回應。<br />\n<br />\n直到記者會結束，有傳媒再問她，為何戴錯口罩都不回應，以及會否擔心有播毒風險，陳肇始無回應就離開。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564220-20201208.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564220-20201208.htm&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W8orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=a1c90461\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564220-20201208.htm&h=c3e33114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564220-20201208.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3a7e549cae05ee25bb5be9af5742a0b68c6ef2ba","tid":2317063,"uid":275498,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 戴左十個月都仲錯 <br />\n<br />\n智商問題"},{"pid":"02782a91b233b64be70759280371d82032ba858e","tid":2317063,"uid":42820,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:56:00.000Z","msg":"陳姑娘個姑娘牌點考番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59fd9d20a3cdbfe24678a023eb4972030cc9bb95","tid":2317063,"uid":57488,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:56:24.000Z","msg":"香港被呢班廢柴管治只有末路"},{"pid":"065744d324edf5fb